Description: This includes infants and toddlers and all pre-kindergarten students who either had an IFSP/IEP or received evaluation services for special education during the fiscal year.
A child enrolled in an Early Education program: School Readiness or Early Childhood Family Education
Students in kindergarten and have an IFSP/IEP, irrespective of the special education program to which they are assigned. HK students should not be included in regular kindergarten.
